        "subject": "LU-XXXX socklnd: Add histograms in /proc",
        "message": "LU-XXXX socklnd: Add histograms in /proc\n\nThis change is intended to increase the visibility into the socklnd layer\nby exporting certain information to /proc. A histogram is exported which\nshows the time tx messages spend queued, waiting to be written to the\nunderlying socket.\n\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I7920797116ad1e7571b0cf0099c081f7502a8a51\n"
